  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat. Brown the lamb in batches, then set aside.",
    "Soften the onion, garlic, and ginger in the pot, then add the Moroccan spice blend.",
    "Return the lamb to the pot and add the coconut milk, chicken broth, and honey.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 2 hours.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste. Serve hot over couscous or rice."
